                <sec_caption/>
                <sec_txt>
                    <h3>ISTH Guidance Statement
                        <sup type="ref">[11]</sup>
                    </h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The term 
                            <em>suggest</em> has a specific meaning in the guidelines
                        </li>
                        <li>The Hokusai VTE Cancer study carefully captured the different chemotherapeutic or biological agents being used by patients

                            <ul>
                                <li>A wide array of different agents was used, and there did not seem to be a problem with them</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </sec_txt>
